      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving precision, featuring the S54 3.2L inline-six engine with high-pressure Double VANOS and individual throttle bodies. The powertrain is paired with a Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox and a variable M-differential lock for optimal power delivery. This specimen is mechanically flawless, featuring documented rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension geometry remains tight, providing the sharp turn-in and communicative feedback synonymous with this chassis. With zero clear coat failure and an immaculate underside, this collector-grade vehicle is ready for the most discerning purist.",
